{{Top|leg}}
'''Engine tape''' was a highly-adaptable adhesive that was produced in rolled strips. It was often considered one of the most vital things for a [[Starship/Legends|starship]] mechanic to possess within their arsenal of tools and equipment. Quite often [[Spacer/Legends|spacers]] would joke about complex repair jobs having to rely on "engine tape and faith in [[The Force/Legends|the Force]]" for completion in an emergency situation.{{Tech-stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
It is functionally identical to [[mesh tape]], [[space tape]], and [[Spacer's tape/Legends|spacer's tape]], which are all virtually identical to the real world's duct tape.

